                     <interp inst="t18450707-1521-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for breaking and entering a certain building within the curtilage of the dwelling-house of <persName id="t18450707-name-380" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450707-name-380" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
