                        <interp inst="t18450707-name-384" type="given" value="JOB"></interp>JOB READ</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Hawes, a pawnbroker, in Old-street. This apron was pawned in the name of John Douglas—I do not know who by.</p>
